=====================
doveadm-cluster-geodb
=====================


NAME
====

doveadm-cluster-geodb - Utility actions for Dovecot Cluster GeoDB


SYNOPSIS
========

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster geodb refresh


DESCRIPTION
===========

**doveadm cluster geodb** can be used to run actions that interact with and
modify Dovecot Cluster GeoDB.

.. include:: global-options.inc


COMMANDS
========


cluster geodb refresh
---------------------

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] cluster geodb refresh

Refreshes local caches from GeoDB. This is mainly intended for testing purposes.
Usually this is not necessary to run, because cluster has been designed to work
correctly even when caches aren't up-to-date.


